Careers
If you are seeking a career in private wealth management, please contact us. To succeed at Ballentine Partners you need excellent problem-solving skills, communication skills, project management skills, attention to accuracy, integrity, and high emotional intelligence. Prior experience in private wealth management or a related field is a plus, but not essential.
Senior members of the firm come from diverse backgrounds, including investment management, corporate strategy consulting, corporate finance, family business experience, and public accounting.
The primary career paths within our company are: (1) investment analysis and management, and (2) financial planning and wealth management.
To learn more about how we create career paths, please see the article Pipeline to Empowerment. To view our current openings and apply please visit our Career Portal.


Investment Offerings
We are always interested in reviewing information on investment offerings to determine if they are appropriate for our clients. If you would like us to learn more about your firm or offerings, please send information by email at investments@ballentinepartners.com to our investment team.






